data.description: Discover luxury living at its finest in this expansive home spanning over 2500 square feet. As you approach, you're greeted by a charming courtyard in the front yard, setting the stage for the elegance that awaits within. Inside, versatility abounds with a flex media/extra room space, offering endless possibilities for customization to suit your lifestyle. Hosting gatherings is a breeze in the huge formal dining room, which can effortlessly transition to accommodate various purposes, from entertaining guests to serving as a creative workspace. With four bedrooms and three bathrooms, there's plenty of room for everyone to unwind and recharge. Indulge in the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality - schedule your tour today and make this Southeast Visalia gem your own! Bed count is different than tax records. Buyer to verify.
